  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Visual Novel Writer & Illustrator",
  "description": "<p><strong>About Yuusoft and RouteVN</strong></p><p>- Yuusoft Pte. Ltd. is a company incorporated in Singapore</p><p>- Yuusoft Pte. Ltd. is the company that builds and operates RouteVN</p><p>- RouteVN is a dedicated platform for Visual Novels. We build tools and technology to create, distribute and read Visual Novels</p><p></p><p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><p>- We're looking for a rare talent who can handle both creative writing and visual illustration</p><p>- You will be using RouteVN's product to create meaningful free-to-play Visual Novels</p><p>- Ideate and discuss with the team to come up with Visual Novel concepts</p><p>- Writing: craft compelling narratives, develop world-building elements, write engaging dialogue, and create memorable characters</p><p>- Illustration: design expressive character sprites, create immersive backgrounds, UI elements, and CG illustrations for key scenes</p><p></p><p><strong>What an ideal candidate looks like</strong></p><p>- You have a genuine passion for Visual Novels and storytelling</p><p>- You genuinely enjoy writing and drawing all day</p><p>- You have a portfolio demonstrating your writing and illustration skills</p><p>- You are curious, a fast learner, and enjoy creative collaboration</p><p>- You are able to work with a team and meet deadlines</p><p>- You are able to work independently, take your own initiatives and responsibilities</p><p></p><p><strong>Application and selection process</strong></p><p>- Application form submission</p><p>- Video Interview</p><p>- Take home assignment</p><p>- Paid work trial</p><p></p>",
